00:16:07,180 --> 00:16:09,060
Congratulations, Miss Jiugong

284
00:16:09,060 --> 00:16:11,220
You are the school's top 60 girl now

285
00:16:12,720 --> 00:16:14,270
What a surprise

286
00:16:14,270 --> 00:16:15,890
We have a new top girl on the first day of the new semester

287
00:16:16,430 --> 00:16:17,310
However

288
00:16:17,890 --> 00:16:18,930
I made this

289
00:16:20,850 --> 00:16:21,470
This is...

290
00:16:25,060 --> 00:16:26,680
I thought it was something extraordinary

291
00:16:26,850 --> 00:16:29,640
Most cultivators train very hard

292
00:16:30,100 --> 00:16:32,220
They usually don't eat anything for months

293
00:16:32,220 --> 00:16:33,890
even for years.

294
00:16:34,470 --> 00:16:37,100
The higher the stage they reach

295
00:16:37,100 --> 00:16:39,720
the less sensitive they are to smells or tastes

296
00:16:40,720 --> 00:16:42,930
For someone as great as Wang Ling

297
00:16:42,930 --> 00:16:45,640
all good food will be bland

298
00:16:46,600 --> 00:16:48,520
The only thing that can impress Wang Ling

299
00:16:49,350 --> 00:16:50,270
is...

300
00:16:52,310 --> 00:16:53,310
mouth taste

301
00:16:56,770 --> 00:16:59,390
Teacher, we agreed on three days

302
00:16:59,390 --> 00:17:01,180
But it's been three days

303
00:17:01,180 --> 00:17:03,470
How long do you want me to do this, Teacher?

304
00:17:04,220 --> 00:17:06,720
Small Raccoon Crispy Noodles

305
00:17:07,560 --> 00:17:09,770
Lingling. Lingling

306
00:17:09,770 --> 00:17:10,970
Your Crispy Noodles

307
00:17:42,970 --> 00:17:45,810
The result is clear now

308
00:17:45,810 --> 00:17:47,970
I don't accept. Why?

309
00:17:48,430 --> 00:17:49,470
Jiugong

310
00:17:49,470 --> 00:17:51,770
You don't know at all what Senior Wang Ling wants

311
00:17:52,810 --> 00:17:53,520
Look?

312
00:17:53,890 --> 00:17:56,390
Senior Wang Ling only took one mouthful of your noodles

313
00:17:57,350 --> 00:17:58,140
What?

314
00:17:58,890 --> 00:18:00,930
Crispy noodles soaked in water

315
00:18:00,930 --> 00:18:03,600
whatever soup and superior ingredients you use

316
00:18:03,600 --> 00:18:05,970
doesn't take long to give the same mouth taste as crispy noodles

317
00:18:06,720 --> 00:18:07,810
Look at Senior Wang

318
00:18:08,430 --> 00:18:09,680
How is he enjoying it

319
00:18:10,220 --> 00:18:11,220
now i announce

320
00:18:11,220 --> 00:18:12,810
the winner for the top girl title is...

321
00:18:12,810 --> 00:18:15,390
Sun Rong

322
00:18:15,390 --> 00:18:16,970
She's cheating

323
00:18:16,970 --> 00:18:18,680
This is not fair. This is not fair

324
00:18:21,890 --> 00:18:23,810
Senior Wang Ling, we have class later this afternoon

325
00:18:23,810 --> 00:18:24,810
Let's go

326
00:18:25,390 --> 00:18:28,890
Jiugong's first attempt to subdue Huaxiu failed

327
00:18:28,890 --> 00:18:30,810
Stories tell us

328
00:18:30,810 --> 00:18:32,520
that sometimes the simplest way is needed

329
00:18:32,520 --> 00:18:35,600
to cook excellent food

330
00:18:36,180 --> 00:18:38,220
No fancy cuisine

331
00:18:38,220 --> 00:18:42,180
can match a sincere heart

332
00:18:44,254 --> 00:18:51,404
Subtitle by Kingcastillo, thank you for faithfully watching

